+## Project Organization
+
+### Recommended File Structure for Convex
+
+```
+convex/
+├── schema.ts                 # Table definitions
+├── init.ts                   # Seeding function (official pattern)
+├── tasksQuery.ts            # All task queries exported
+├── tasksMutation.ts         # All task mutations exported
+├── projectsQuery.ts         # All project queries
+├── projectsMutation.ts      # All project mutations
+├── labelsQuery.ts           # Label queries
+├── labelsMutation.ts        # Label mutations
+└── tsconfig.json            # TypeScript config
+
+src/
+└── hooks/
+    ├── useTasks.ts          # Custom hooks for task operations
+    ├── useProjects.ts       # Custom hooks for projects
+    ├── useLabels.ts         # Custom hooks for labels
+    └── index.ts             # Export all hooks
+```
+
+**Key points:**
+- ✅ Flat structure (no nested `queries/`, `mutations/` folders) - avoids API generation issues
+- ✅ File naming: `[domain]Query.ts` and `[domain]Mutation.ts`
+- ✅ One domain per file for organization
+- ✅ Auto-generates API structure:
+  - `api.tasksQuery.list`
+  - `api.tasksMutation.create`
+
+**Avoid:**
+- ❌ Subdirectories (breaks API generation)
+- ❌ Mixing queries and mutations in one file
+- ❌ Long filenames - keep it simple
